; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; (Priority 3) - Cheating
; Description: The AI is given resources of each type. More/Less depends on difficulty.
; ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
; Note: Edited for difficulty:
; Hardest - 2000, 30,000
; Hard - 1000, 15,000
; Moderate - 500, 7,500
; Easy - 250, 3,750
; Easiest - 125, 1,875
